<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1437,151,2035]" pageId="13" pageNumber="76">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,335,1902,1927]" pageId="13" pageNumber="76">Comments.</emphasis>
Based upon the colour of pubescence, the male of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Schwarz" baseAuthorityYear="1939" box="[944,1097,1902,1927]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Lepidotrigona" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="76" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="doipaensis">
<emphasis box="[944,1097,1902,1927]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="76">L. doipaensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
might be misidentified as 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Lepidotrigona" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="76" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavibasis">
<emphasis box="[1413,1428,1904,1927]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="76">L</emphasis>
